org.afplib.afplib

Interface CDD

  • All Superinterfaces:
    org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier, SF
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    CDDImpl

    public interface CDD
extends SF
    A representation of the model object 'CDD'.

    The following features are supported:

    • Xoc Base
    • Yoc Base
    • Xoc Units
    • Yoc Units
    • Xoc Size
    • Yoc Size
    • Triplets

    See Also:
    AfplibPackage.getCDD()
